  "text": "Effect of P addition. The observed strong microbial responses to P addition are in line with the results of previous experiments in other tropical lowland forest in France Guiana, Costa Rica, and Panama [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] 40 . There are several mechanisms that cause P limitation in terrestrial ecosystems. In the present study, the N deposition reaches 30-70 kg N ha",
